{"tid":88532,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今次水洗都唔清了","createTime":"2017-01-20T16:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T06:54:42.000Z","uid":3870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f00050aa7571f3ecdaa4951037e2d51cb6f8c97","tid":88532,"uid":3870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"背景:<br />\n我同女友拍拖5年多  佢係我初戀<br />\n我仲讀緊u  佢岀黎做野幾個月 同齡<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n今日夜晚如常咁食晚飯，行街拍拖<br />\n食完飯之後，身為好男人既我就拎包紙巾岀黎大家抹嘴。點知一打開包紙巾，就發現有條長頭髮癡住係上面。之後當然佢係嬲左我，我點跪玻璃都無用。<br />\n我一萬個%無接觸過女仔，我自己係個n展毒丁，唔高又唔靚仔，自邊一個女仔fd都無，絕對無做過對唔住女友既事，我完全唔知條頭髮點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人話我知我要點證明俾佢睇我無講大話/點令佢信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dddc0046ec99e9ec7b9d15f668fe5108d0ccb68","tid":88532,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"老母條頭髮"},{"pid":"c909ccbea5bdfdeac0468b62f84df34ded62a193","tid":88532,"uid":3870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母條頭髮</blockquote><br />\n我淨係諗過會唔會前排剪頭髮果陣癡番黎/之前食飯放係枱面癡到。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db57d3e50996f3aa555f50099a7e6310f1fe6d94","tid":88532,"uid":3870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff68d30165be2f2d7008e227c8cf2d80dfe5615","tid":88532,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3447e19fbeb0c1ff8aea90c31a492dc62ba48aa2","tid":88532,"uid":3870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ab35ebc7700e676f948750532a74d05b4c1d97","tid":88532,"uid":3870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea579ea8ec97988bf16738a3b5bb26185f3342f","tid":88532,"uid":77971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會為左條頭髮嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73e9b41b4e2f52e28a922217cce4252a4bfbdd2","tid":88532,"uid":3870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會為左條頭髮嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次真係因爲佢以為我去左識女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842ebf5b5e0afd7e27da3f2c32dc200bfdb63e52","tid":88532,"uid":32795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}